pl.edu.agh.jdziennik.model

Class WeekTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.agh.jdziennik.model.WeekTerm

  • @Entity
public class WeekTerm
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a term in a week when a subject is taught to a class. This class is mapped by hibernate.
